{"tid":999834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TSMC 台積電再度出現生產事故 – 過萬片晶圓或被污染，16 / 12 nm 產能受損","createTime":"2019-01-29T04:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T08:34:24.000Z","uid":15564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a66eb57bb90a9435cf65cfef65db67f6cf4d3ee5","tid":999834,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2019/01/TSMC-chemical-defect-Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2019%2F01%2FTSMC-chemical-defect-Cover.jpg&h=92d34e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於去年台積電創始人張忠謀退休後，台積電改為雙 CEO 管理體制。不過在劉德音、魏哲家接手後，就爆出一次生產安全事故，去年新竹、南科的晶圓廠被病毒攻擊，損失了 26 億新台幣。今天台積電 Fab 14B  廠被爆出一次安全事故，這次是晶圓被不合格原料污染，預計損失過萬片晶圓，影響的是主力營收的 16 / 12 nm 製程生產線，NVIDIA GPU 以及多家手機晶片廠商都在使用這工藝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2019/01/tsmc-Pollution.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2019%2F01%2Ftsmc-Pollution.jpg&h=378c814f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息指台積電南科晶圓廠發生了晶圓污染事件，使晶圓報廢，正在統計損失中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.xfast-hosting.com/2019/01/TSMC-FAB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.xfast-hosting.com%2F2019%2F01%2FTSMC-FAB.jpg&h=390e0ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前台積電還在確認影響有多大，暫時也沒有公佈影響。不過 16 / 12 nm 製程是台積電的主力營收來源之一，NVIDIA GPU 晶片、Hisilicon、MediaTek 的手機晶片以及一些 ARM Server 處理器都使用了這製程，是否會影響供貨還不得而知。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/23131/tsmc-chemical-defect/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F23131%2Ftsmc-chemical-defect%2F&d=kLXyKWzv0KFRbXtH0eH7a9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c94fcf40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/23131/tsmc-chemical-defect/</a>"},{"pid":"51b8a876f1aca027f44f7663601b83c18a182bef","tid":999834,"uid":15564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">市場傳出，出包的是光阻液，台積電主要供應商有日商信越、JSR 與陶氏化學等三家。</span><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/52115/tsmc-fab-14b-yield-rate-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F52115%2Ftsmc-fab-14b-yield-rate-&d=kLXyKWzv0KFRbXtH0eH7a9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=12eb9335\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/52115/tsmc-fab-14b-yield-rate-</a>"},{"pid":"841603b432690bdcf592769907050e608c3ff774","tid":999834,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"係時候賣畀支那"},{"pid":"cd7dd7de8aa5086a77a64809d6c281fa03382d9f","tid":999834,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"Hisilicon<br />\n<br />\n海思?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c6657f5e0a36963d268e073717814aed619a9a","tid":999834,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"Hisilicon、MediaTek <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海思就海思，聯發科就聯發科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6adea04bc309663776728635082fda2fa298ef","tid":999834,"uid":82717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"TSMC搞單咁嘅野，唔知依個會唔會係可以cut單的借口呢？"},{"pid":"c4b2523ed517e982469d0754892ea015507ded19","tid":999834,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22c6657f5e0a36963d268e073717814aed619a9a","tid":999834,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"Hisilicon、MediaTek <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海思就海思，聯發科就聯發科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"海思無貨咁華為用乜CPU出電話好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm